headline: Apartments.com Releases Multifamily Rent Growth Report for Second Quarter of 2025
summary: ARLINGTON, Va., July 07, 2025--The national year-over-year asking rent growth for apartments was 0.9% in the second quarter of 2025, slightly slower than the 1.2% recorded in the first quarter. From mid-2023, year-over-year rent growth hovered between 1.0% and 1.2% after its rapid deceleration in 2021 and 2022. This was the first easing of rent growth since the first quarter of 2024.
